postLogEntry: Arbiter Brokstrom has announced the addition of both naval and ground forces to the United Coalition -- forces to help protect our people from threats internal and external.
The Era of United Coalition consolidation has come to a close. The Arbiter Brokstrom has tightened her grip of control and the new United Defense Force and navy give the union even more power.

Councilor Brace Whitclaire of De Valtos and Councilor Brigatta von Sha of Thulun have released a report showing the Arbiter's involvement with one of the Gux Mastermind Cult. The evidence holds that she paid the Gux to assassinate a Moklumnue Prince and his entire family.

blockName: ERA: UCF FLEET IS NOW AVAILABLE
postLogEntry: We encountered our first United Coalition military officer today in the void as we entered a system. Of course, the captain demanded to search our ship for contraband.
Arbiter Estelle Brokstrom has ended her time as the Magnate of the United Coalition, stepping aside due to the stain of Gux Miga on her pristine record.

blockName: One Year Warning on End of Dissension
postLogEntry: The new leadership of the United Coalition is likely to be decided within the year. In a move designed to win faction support, Whitclaire and von Sha have openly released designs for new powerful, level 8 ship weaponry of all patterns designed by the Coalition's previously unmentioned research division.
A new generation of level 8 ship weaponry of all patterns has been released by the United Coalition's previously unmentioned research division and shared with all factions.
